<!DOCTYPE html>
<html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40" lang="uz">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Sillabus — {{sillabus.f_nomi}}</title>
<style>
  @page Section1 {
    size: 21cm 29.7cm;
    margin: 2cm 2cm 2cm 2cm;
    mso-header-margin: 1cm;
    mso-footer-margin: 1cm;
    mso-footer: url("file:///C:/sillabus/sillabus_files/header.htm") f1;
  }
  div.Section1 { page: Section1; }
  body { font-family: "Times New Roman", serif; font-size: 13pt; margin: 0; color: #000; line-height: 1; }
  h2, h3, h4 { text-align: center; font-weight: bold; }
  h3 { font-size: 14pt; text-transform: uppercase; margin: 14px 0 4px; }
  h4 { font-size: 13pt; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  h5 { text-align: center; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold; margin: 14px 0 6px; }
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12pt; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #000; padding: 5px 7px; vertical-align: top; mso-para-margin:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt; }
  .thead-row { background: #e0e0e0; }
  tfoot tr { background: #e0e0e0; font-weight: bold; }
  .group-header td { background: #e0e0e0; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; }
  .center { text-align: center; }
  .right { text-align: right; }
  .bold { font-weight: bold; }
  .small { font-size: 11pt; }
  .justify { text-align: justify; }
  ul, ol { margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; }
  li { margin: 0; mso-para-margin-top: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 0cm; }
  hr { border: none; border-top: 1px solid #999; margin: 14px 0; }
  .sign-table td { border: none; padding: 4px 8px; }
  .no-border td { border: none; padding: 2px 7px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="Section1">

{{!-- Sarlavha --}}
<table class="no-border">
  <tr>
    <td style="width:60%; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; padding:8px;">
      {{#if tashkilot.logo}}
      <img src="{{baseUrl}}/uploads/{{tashkilot.logo}}" alt="Logo" style="max-width:180px; max-height:100px;">
      {{/if}}
    </td>
    <td style="width:40%; vertical-align:top; padding:8px; text-align:center; color:#1a4f91; font-size:13pt;">
      <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; line-height:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly; font-weight:bold;">
        {{#if tashkilot.tashkilot_nomi}}{{tashkilot.tashkilot_nomi}}{{else}}Universitet{{/if}}<br>
        Akademik ishlar boʻyicha<br>
        prorektor {{#if tashkilot.masul}}{{tashkilot.masul}}{{else}}_________________{{/if}}<br>
        <br>
        _______________________________<br>
        {{#if sillabus.yil_nomi}}{{firstYear sillabus.yil_nomi}}{{else}}20___{{/if}} yil &ldquo;______&rdquo; ___________
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h3 style="font-size:13pt;">{{sillabus.f_nomi}}</h3>
<h4 style="font-size:13pt;">FANNING OʻQUV DASTURI (SILLABUS)</h4>

{{!-- Maʻlumotlar jadvali --}}
<table style="font-size:13pt; mso-para-margin:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt; line-height:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly;">
  <tr>
    <td class="bold" valign="middle" align="left" style="width:25%; text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Akademik daraja</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="width:22%; vertical-align:middle;">{{#if sillabus.grade}}{{capitalize sillabus.grade}}{{else}}Bakalavr{{/if}}</td>
    <td valign="middle" align="center" style="width:22%; vertical-align:middle; font-weight:bold;">Taʻlim yoʻnalishi</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="width:31%; vertical-align:middle;">{{#if sillabus.t_yunalish.length}}{{#each sillabus.t_yunalish}}{{this}}<br>{{/each}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bold" valign="middle" align="left" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Fan kodi</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{sillabus.fan_kodi}}</td>
    <td valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle; font-weight:bold;">Taʻlim shakli</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if sillabus.t_shakli}}{{capitalize sillabus.t_shakli}}{{else}}Kunduzgi{{/if}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bold" valign="middle" align="left" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Semestr</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if sillabus.semestr}}{{sillabus.semestr}}-semestr{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
    <td valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle; font-weight:bold;">Modulning davomiyligi</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if sillabus.davomiyligi}}{{sillabus.davomiyligi}} hafta{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bold" valign="middle" align="left" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Kredit hajmi</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if sillabus.ects}}ECTS: {{sillabus.ects}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
    <td valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle; font-weight:bold;">Tayyorladi</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if tashkilot.short_name}}{{tashkilot.short_name}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="bold" valign="middle" align="left" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Ajratilgan akademik soat hajmi</td>
    <td valign="middle" style="padding:0; vertical-align:middle;">
      <table style="margin-bottom:0; mso-para-margin:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;">
        <tr><td class="center" align="center" style="border:none; border-bottom:1px solid #000;">{{sum sillabus.auditoriya_soat sillabus.mustaqil_soat}}</td></tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="border:none; padding:0;">
            <table style="margin-bottom:0; mso-para-margin:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;">
              <tr>
                <td class="center" align="center" style="width:50%; border-top:none; border-left:none; border-bottom:none;">{{#if sillabus.auditoriya_soat}}{{sillabus.auditoriya_soat}}{{else}}0{{/if}}<br>(aud)</td>
                <td class="center" align="center" style="width:50%; border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">{{#if sillabus.mustaqil_soat}}{{sillabus.mustaqil_soat}}{{else}}0{{/if}}<br>(must)</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td>
    <td valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle; font-weight:bold;">Talabalarni erkin qabul qilish kuni</td>
    <td class="center" valign="middle" align="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if sillabus.talabalarni_qabul_kuni}}{{sillabus.talabalarni_qabul_kuni}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin:0; font-size:13pt; line-height:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly;">&nbsp;</p>

<table class="no-border" style="width:100%; margin:0; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; font-size:13pt; mso-para-margin:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;">
  <tr>
    <td style="width:20%; vertical-align:top;"><strong>Tuzuvchi:</strong></td>
    <td style="vertical-align:top; line-height:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly;">
      <p style="margin:0;"><strong>{{#if sillabus.tuzuvchi_fish}}{{sillabus.tuzuvchi_fish}}{{else}}{{#if sillabus.oqituvchi_nomi}}{{sillabus.oqituvchi_nomi}}{{else}}{{sillabus.oqituvchi_login}}{{/if}}{{/if}}</strong></p>
      {{#if sillabus.tuzuvchi_lavozim}}<p style="margin:0;">{{sillabus.tuzuvchi_lavozim}}</p>{{/if}}
      {{#if sillabus.tuzuvchi_tel}}<p style="margin:0;">Tel: {{sillabus.tuzuvchi_tel}}</p>{{/if}}
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

{{#if taqrizchilar.length}}
<table class="no-border" style="width:100%; margin:10pt 0 0; mso-table-lspace:0pt; mso-table-rspace:0pt; font-size:13pt; mso-para-margin:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;">
  <tr>
    <td style="width:20%; vertical-align:top;"><strong>Taqrizchilar:</strong></td>
    <td style="vertical-align:top; line-height:100%; mso-line-height-rule:exactly;">
      {{#each taqrizchilar}}
      <p style="margin:0;"><strong>{{this.tartib}}. {{this.fish}}</strong></p>
      {{#if this.lavozim}}<p style="margin:0;">{{this.lavozim}}</p>{{/if}}
      {{/each}}
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
{{/if}}

{{#if sillabus.majlis_raqami}}
<p class="justify" style="margin-top:60pt; margin-bottom:0; text-indent:2em; font-size:13pt;">
  Ushbu fan sillabusi {{#if tashkilot.tashkilot_nomi}}{{tashkilot.tashkilot_nomi}}{{else}}Universitet{{/if}}
  Kengashining {{#if sillabus.majlis_sanasi}}{{sanaYil sillabus.majlis_sanasi}} yil {{sanaKunOy sillabus.majlis_sanasi}}{{/if}}
  {{sillabus.majlis_raqami}}-son majlisida muhokama qilingan.
</p>
{{/if}}

{{!-- ===================== 2-BET ===================== --}}
<br clear=all style='mso-special-character:line-break;page-break-before:always'>

<h5 style="font-size:13pt;">Fan boʻyicha talabaning bilimi, koʻnikmasi va<br>malakasiga qoʻyilgan talablar</h5>
<p class="justify" style="font-size:13pt; font-weight:bold; margin:0 0 4pt;">Mazkur fanni oʻrganish davomida talaba:</p>
{{#if sillabus.bilim_ko_nikma}}
{{#each (splitLines sillabus.bilim_ko_nikma)}}
<p class="justify" style="font-size:13pt; margin:0 0 4pt; text-indent:1em;">– {{this}}{{#if @last}}.{{else}};{{/if}}</p>
{{/each}}
{{else}}
<p class="center" style="color:#666;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}

<p class="justify">
  <strong>Fanga ajratilgan soatlar.</strong>
  Fanga ajratilgan umumiy soatlar hajmi {{sum sillabus.auditoriya_soat sillabus.mustaqil_soat}} akademik soat boʻlib,
  shundan auditoriya mashgʻulotlari {{#if sillabus.auditoriya_soat}}{{sillabus.auditoriya_soat}}{{else}}0{{/if}} soatni,
  mustaqil taʻlim {{#if sillabus.mustaqil_soat}}{{sillabus.mustaqil_soat}}{{else}}0{{/if}} soatni tashkil etadi.
  {{#if maruzaRows.length}}
  Auditoriya mashgʻulotlarida jami {{totalJami maruzaRows}} soat ({{auditoriyaSoatIzoh maruzaRows}}) fan mavzulari oʻqitiladi va oraliq, yakuniy imtihonlar uchun 2 soatdan jami 4 soat vaqt ajratilgan.
  {{/if}}
</p>

<p style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold; margin:0 0 4pt; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:4pt;">Fanni oʻzlashtirish va mustaqil oʻqib-oʻrganish uchun<br>asosiy adabiyotlar roʻyxati:</p>
{{#if (splitLines sillabus.asosiy_adabiyotlar)}}
<ol>{{#each (splitLines sillabus.asosiy_adabiyotlar)}}<li>{{this}}</li>{{/each}}</ol>
{{else}}
<p class="center" style="color:#666;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold; margin:0 0 4pt; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:4pt;">Fanni oʻzlashtirish uchun<br>qoʻshimcha adabiyotlar roʻyxati:</p>
{{#if (splitLines sillabus.qoshimcha_adabiyotlar)}}
<ol>{{#each (splitLines sillabus.qoshimcha_adabiyotlar)}}<li>{{this}}</li>{{/each}}</ol>
{{else}}
<p class="center" style="color:#666;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}

<p style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold; margin:0 0 4pt; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:4pt;">Internet manzillar:</p>
{{#if (splitLines sillabus.internet_manzillar)}}
<ol>{{#each (splitLines sillabus.internet_manzillar)}}<li>{{this}}</li>{{/each}}</ol>
{{else}}
<p class="center" style="color:#666;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}

{{!-- ===================== 3-BET ===================== --}}
<br clear=all style='mso-special-character:line-break;page-break-before:always'>

{{!-- Maʻruza va amaliy mashgʻulotlarining rejasi --}}
<h5>Maʻruza va amaliy mashgʻulotlarining rejasi</h5>
{{#if maruzaRows.length}}
<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr class="thead-row">
      <th class="center" style="width:5%;">№</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:22%;">Mavzular</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:43%;">Dars mazmuni</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:10%;">Maʻruza soat</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:10%;">Amaliy soat</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:10%;">Jami soat</th>
    </tr>
    {{#each maruzaRows}}
    <tr>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.tartib_raqam}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;"><strong>{{this.mavzu}}</strong></td>
      <td>{{#if this.dars_mazmuni.length}}<ul>{{#each this.dars_mazmuni}}<li>{{this}}</li>{{/each}}</ul>{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.maruza_soat}}</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.amaliy_soat}}</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{sum this.maruza_soat this.amaliy_soat}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="3" class="center">Jami:</td>
      <td class="center">{{totalMaruza maruzaRows}}</td>
      <td class="center">{{totalAmaliy maruzaRows}}</td>
      <td class="center">{{totalJami maruzaRows}}</td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
{{else}}
<p class="center" style="color:#666;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}

{{!-- Mustaqil taʻlim rejasi --}}
<h5>Mustaqil taʻlim mashgʻulotlari rejasi</h5>
{{#if mustaqilRows.length}}
<table>
  <tbody>
    <tr class="thead-row">
      <th class="center" style="width:5%;"></th>
      <th class="center" style="width:45%;">Mavzu</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:38%;">Topshiriq</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:12%;">Soat</th>
    </tr>
    {{#each mustaqilRows}}
    <tr>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.tartib_raqam}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;"><strong>{{this.mavzu}}</strong></td>
      <td>{{#if this.topshiriq}}{{#each (splitLetterItems this.topshiriq)}}<p style="margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;">{{this}}</p>{{/each}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.soat}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
  <tfoot>
    <tr>
      <td colspan="3" class="center">Jami</td>
      <td class="center">{{totalSoat mustaqilRows}}</td>
    </tr>
  </tfoot>
</table>
{{else}}
<p class="center" style="color:#666;">Maʻlumot kiritilmagan</p>
{{/if}}

{{!-- Baholash mezoni (foiz) --}}
<h5 style="margin-top:20px; margin-bottom:0; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;">FANNI BAHOLASH MEZONI VA REJASI</h5>
<p style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;">Talabalar bilimini baholash turlari.</p>
{{#if (eq sillabus.t_shakli "sirtqi")}}
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;">Mazkur fandan talabalar bilimini baholashda 2 ta nazorat turidan foydalaniladi. Joriy baholash (JB) va yakuniy imtihon (YI).</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>Joriy baholash (JB):</strong> Ushbu nazorat turi semestr davomida toʻplanib boriladi va quyidagilardan tarkib topadi:</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>Vazifa/topshiriqlar.</strong> Har bir talaba individual tarzda oʻqituvchi tomonidan berilgan vazifa/masala/topshiriqni bajaradi. Shuningdek, mustaqil taʻlim topshiriqlarini koʻrsatma boʻyicha bajaradi.</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>Yakuniy imtihon (YI).</strong> Modulning oxirgi haftasida (25 yoki 50) test shaklida amalga oshiriladi.</p>
{{else}}
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;">Mazkur fandan talabalar bilimini baholashda joriy baholash (JB), oraliq imtihon (OI) va yakuniy imtihon (YI) turlaridan foydalaniladi.</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>Joriy baholash (JB):</strong> ushbu baholash turi 3 ta yoʻnalishda amalga oshiriladi:</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>1) Darsga qatnashish (DV)</strong>: talabaning dars mashgʻulotlariga kelishi.</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>2) Dars mashgʻulotlaridagi faollik</strong>: talabaning maʻruza va seminar mashgʻulotlaridagi faolligi.</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>3) Mustaqil taʻlim</strong>: Har bir talaba individual tarzda mustaqil taʻlim topshiriqlarini mazkur sillabusda qayd etilgan shakllarda bajaradi.</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>Oraliq imtihon (OI).</strong> Ushbu imtihon turi semestr davomida bir marta olinadi (8-haftada) fan (modul)ning oʻtilgan mavzulari asosida qisqa savol-javob yozma shaklda olinadi. Masofaviy taʻlim uchun oraliq imtihonlari test shaklida olinadi.</p>
<p class="justify" style="text-indent:2em; margin:0; mso-para-margin-top:0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;"><strong>Yakuniy imtihon (YI).</strong> Ushbu imtihon turi semestrning 16-haftasida (yakuniy imtihonlarga ajratilgan haftada) fan (modul)ning oʻtilgan barcha mavzulari doirasida yozma shaklda amalga oshiriladi. Masofaviy taʻlim uchun yakuniy imtihon test shaklida olinadi.</p>
{{/if}}
{{#if mezoniRows.length}}
<h5 style="font-size:13pt;">Fanni baholash mezoni va rejasi</h5>
<table style="font-size:13pt;">
  {{#each mezoniRows}}
  <tr>
    <td>{{this.nomi}}{{#if this.izoh}} — <em>{{this.izoh}}</em>{{/if}}</td>
    <td style="width:15%; text-align:center; font-weight:bold;">{{cleanNum this.foiz}} %</td>
  </tr>
  {{/each}}
</table>
{{/if}}

{{!-- Talabalar baholash --}}
<h5 style="font-size:13pt;">Talabalar bilimini baholash mezoni</h5>
<table style="font-size:13pt;">
  <tbody>
    <tr style="background:#ffffff;">
      <th class="center" style="width:5%; vertical-align:middle;">№</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:25%; vertical-align:middle;">Nazorat turlari</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:32%; vertical-align:middle;">Izoh</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:15%; vertical-align:middle;">Ball</th>
      <th class="center" style="width:23%; white-space:nowrap; vertical-align:middle;">Oʻtkazilish vaqti</th>
    </tr>
    {{#if jbRows.length}}
    <tr class="group-header">
      <td colspan="5">Joriy baholash (JB)</td>
    </tr>
    {{#each jbRows}}
    <tr>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{increment @index}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.nazorat_nomi}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if this.izoh}}{{this.izoh}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
      <td style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.ball}}</td>
      <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{#if this.otkazilish_vaqti}}{{withHafta this.otkazilish_vaqti}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
    <tr style="background:#ffffff; font-weight:bold;">
      <td colspan="3" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Jami</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{totalBall jbRows}}</td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if oiRows.length}}
    <tr class="group-header">
      <td colspan="5">Oraliq imtihon (OI)</td>
    </tr>
    {{#each oiRows}}
    <tr>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{increment @index}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.nazorat_nomi}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if this.izoh}}{{this.izoh}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
      <td style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.ball}}</td>
      <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{#if this.otkazilish_vaqti}}{{withHafta this.otkazilish_vaqti}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
    <tr style="background:#ffffff; font-weight:bold;">
      <td colspan="3" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Jami</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{totalBall oiRows}}</td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if yiRows.length}}
    <tr class="group-header">
      <td colspan="5">Yakuniy imtihon (YI)</td>
    </tr>
    {{#each yiRows}}
    <tr>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{increment @index}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;">{{this.nazorat_nomi}}</td>
      <td style="vertical-align:middle;">{{#if this.izoh}}{{this.izoh}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
      <td style="text-align:center; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:middle;">{{this.ball}}</td>
      <td style="text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;">{{#if this.otkazilish_vaqti}}{{withHafta this.otkazilish_vaqti}}{{else}}—{{/if}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/each}}
    <tr style="background:#ffffff; font-weight:bold;">
      <td colspan="3" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Jami</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{totalBall yiRows}}</td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if (or jbRows.length oiRows.length yiRows.length)}}
    <tr style="font-weight:bold;">
      <td colspan="3" style="text-align:left; vertical-align:middle;">Umumiy</td>
      <td class="center" style="vertical-align:middle;">{{totalBallAll jbRows oiRows yiRows}}</td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
  </tbody>
</table>

<h5 style="text-transform:uppercase; margin-top:13pt; margin-bottom:0; mso-para-margin-top:13pt; mso-para-margin-bottom:0cm;">Imtihonga qoʻyilgan talab va koʻrsatmalar</h5>
<table class="no-border">
  <tr>
    <td style="width:50%; vertical-align:top;">
      <ol style="font-size:13pt; font-style:italic; text-align:justify;">
        <li>Talaba imtihon nazorati qoidalarini buzgan hollarda, mazkur fandan imtihon bali bekor qilinishi haqida ogohlantiriladi.</li>
        <li>Komissiya aʻzosi imtihon boshlanishini eʻlon qilgunga qadar imtihon varagʻini ochish taʻqiqlanadi.</li>
        <li>Talaba uyali yoki boshqa aloqa vositalari, gadjetlarni oʻchirib, komissiya aʻzosi koʻrsatmasiga binoan oʻzidan uzoqlikda saqlashi shart. Kitob, manuskript, daftar va boshqa koʻmaklashuvchi materiallardan foydalanish mumkin emas.</li>
        <li>Talabalar bir-biri bilan gaplashishi, imtihon varaqlarini koʻrsatishi, koʻchirtirishi, boshqalarni chalgʻitishi maʻn etiladi.</li>
      </ol>
    </td>
    <td style="width:50%; vertical-align:top;">
      <ol style="font-size:13pt; font-style:italic; text-align:justify;" start="5">
        <li>Oziq-ovqat va ichimliklarni auditoriyaga olib kirishi mumkin emas. Shifokor koʻrsatmasiga binoan dori-darmon, kichik idishdagi suv bundan mustasno.</li>
        <li>Auditoriyadan ruxsatsiz chiqish mumkin emas. Xususan, imtihonning birinchi va oxirgi 10 minutida auditoriyadan chiqish taʻqiqlanadi. Talaba imtihon varaqasini muddatidan oldin topshirib chiqib ketgan holatda qayta auditoriyaga qoʻyilmaydi.</li>
        <li>Komissiya aʻzosi imtihon tugashini eʻlon qilganidan soʻng, talaba yozishni toʻxtatadi va imtihon varaqlari yigʻilgunga qadar auditoriyani tark etmaydi.</li>
      </ol>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h5 style="font-size:13pt;">ECTS kredit taʻlim tizimi asosida baholash tavsifi</h5>
<table style="font-size:13pt;">
